Actress Tayo Odueke aka Sikiratu Sindodo got a pleasant surprise on her birthday thanks to her friends and colleagues in Nollywood. She was woken up by instrumentalists who played birthday tunes while her friends came bearing gifts and balloons to make the birthday a unique one. Sindodo shared some photos from the day and posted: “I’ll put a smile on my face and won’t let the troubles of life get me down because it’s my birthday today. A very happy birthday to me!” She added: “My biggest thanks go to the author of the universe the highest God the one who created me in this special day. I ask Him to bless all my hustles and ease my daily activities. Happy birthday to me!”